# ADMIN USER STORIES & DASHBOARD FUNCTIONALITY

## ADMIN ROLE DEFINITION
The Admin role is primarily held by HR personnel and system administrators who manage the entire feedback ecosystem across the organization. They have full access to configure, monitor, and analyze feedback processes company-wide.

