6. **Notifications Center** - System alerts and user communications

## DETAILED USER STORIES

### ORGANIZATION & USER MANAGEMENT

#### User Story A1: Organization Setup
**As an Admin, I want to set up the organization structure so that feedback cycles can be properly configured with correct reporting relationships.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Create departments and teams with hierarchical structure
- Define reporting relationships between managers and employees
- Import user data from Google Workspace or HRIS systems
- Set organization-wide policies and settings
- Configure workspace domain restrictions for Google OAuth

**Dashboard Features:**
- Organization chart visualization with drag-and-drop editing
- Bulk user import/export functionality with CSV templates
- Department and team management interface with nested structures
- Reporting relationship mapping tool with visual hierarchy
- Integration status monitoring with real-time sync indicators

#### User Story A2: User Role Management
**As an Admin, I want to manage user roles and permissions so that the right people have appropriate access levels.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Assign and modify user roles (Admin, Manager, Employee)
- Manage permission levels for different features
- Handle role transitions (promotions, department changes)
- Audit role changes and access patterns
- Bulk role updates for organizational changes

**Dashboard Features:**
- User roles grid with advanced search and filtering
- Role change history and comprehensive audit trail
- Bulk role assignment tools with CSV upload
- Permission matrix visualization with role comparison
- Active session monitoring with security alerts

#### User Story A3: User Account Management
**As an Admin, I want to manage user accounts and access so that I can control who can use the system and maintain security.**

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Create, activate, deactivate, and delete user accounts
- Reset user passwords and manage authentication issues
- Monitor user login activity and detect suspicious behavior
- Manage Google OAuth domain restrictions and exceptions
- Handle user onboarding and offboarding processes

**Dashboard Features:**
- User account status dashboard with filtering options
- Account lifecycle management with automated workflows
- Login activity monitoring with geographic and device tracking
- Security incident alerts and investigation tools
- Onboarding checklist tracking and completion rates

