- **Cycle Completion Rate**: Target >95% within deadline
- **User Adoption Rate**: Target >90% active users per month
- **System Uptime**: Target >99.9% availability
- **Support Resolution Time**: Target <24 hours for critical issues
- **Data Accuracy**: Target >99% accuracy in reporting
- **User Satisfaction**: Target >4.5/5 in quarterly surveys

### OPERATIONAL METRICS:
- **Average Cycle Setup Time**: Target <2 hours for standard cycles
- **User Onboarding Time**: Target <1 day from account creation to first login
- **Report Generation Speed**: Target <30 seconds for standard reports
- **Data Export Completion**: Target <5 minutes for large datasets
- **Issue Response Time**: Target <2 hours for first response

### SUCCESS INDICATORS:
- Reduced time to complete feedback cycles year-over-year
- Increased quality and depth of feedback content
- Higher user engagement and satisfaction scores
- Improved organizational insights and decision-making capabilities
- Streamlined administrative processes with automation
- Enhanced data-driven talent development programs

